    <h4>IN RE LATIMER. APPEAL FROM THE SUPREME COURT OF ILLINOIS. No. 147, Misc. Decided November 25, 1957.</h4>
    <p>Appeal dismissed and certiorari denied.</p>
    <p>Reported below: <a href="https://law.justia.com/cases/illinois/supreme-court/1957/34278-5.html">11 Ill. 2d 327</a>, <a href="https://law.justia.com/cases/illinois/supreme-court/1957/34278-5.html">143 N.E.2d 20</a>.</p>
